{"id":47794,"date":"2026-01-06T22:36:02","date_gmt":"2026-01-06T21:36:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/?post_type=ajde_events&#038;p=47794"},"modified":"2026-05-10T12:17:40","modified_gmt":"2026-05-10T11:17:40","slug":"trail-bem-viver","status":"publish","type":"ajde_events","link":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/eventos\/trail-bem-viver\/","title":{"rendered":"Trail Bem Viver 2026"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; margin: 20px auto;\">\n  \n  <h2 style=\"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #ff4b2b; padding-left: 15px;\">\n    Resultados\n  <\/h2>\n\n  <div style=\"border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\">\n    \n    <div style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 15px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;\">\n      <div>\n        <span style=\"background: #ff4b2b; color: #fff; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\">Live Results<\/span>\n        <h3 style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">Stop and Go &#8211; Resultados em Direto<\/h3>\n      <\/div>\n      \n      <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/results.stopandgo.pro\/1818\/live\/1\/2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s ease; border: 1px solid #2563eb;\" rel=\"noopener\">\n           Abrir em Ecr\u00e3 Total \u2197\n        <\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 800px; background-color: #fff; position: relative;\">\n      <iframe \n        src=\"https:\/\/results.stopandgo.pro\/1818\/live\/1\/2\" \n        width=\"100%\" \n        height=\"100%\" \n        frameborder=\"0\"\n        style=\"display: block;\"\n        allow=\"clipboard-write\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        title=\"Resultados Stop and Go\">\n      <\/iframe>\n    <\/div>\n    \n    <div style=\"background: #f8fafc; padding: 10px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;\">Cronometragem: <strong>Stop and Go<\/strong><\/span>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\">Atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o autom\u00e1tica<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>O TRAIL BEM VIVER \u00e9 organizado pelo Grupo Desportivo de Magrelos, em parceria com a Junta de Freguesia de Bem Viver e a C\u00e2mara Municipal do Marco de Canaveses.O evento ser\u00e1 realizado no dia e 10 de maio de 2026, no Alto da Forca em Magrelos, na freguesia de Bem Viver, independentemente das condi\u00e7\u00f5es climat\u00e9ricas do dia, desde que a organiza\u00e7\u00e3o entenda que n\u00e3o ofere\u00e7am risco aos participantes. A organiza\u00e7\u00e3o acompanha, em perman\u00eancia a evolu\u00e7\u00e3o das condi\u00e7\u00f5es meteorol\u00f3gicas podendo anular a prova em qualquer altura.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A prova \u00e9 certificada pela Federa\u00e7\u00e3o Portuguesa de Atletismo, ATRP &#8211; Associa\u00e7\u00e3o de Trail Running de Portugal, ITRA &#8211; International Trail Running Association e UTMB \u2013 Ultra Trail Mont Blanc.<br>O Trail Bem Viver ser\u00e1 constitu\u00eddo por quatro provas:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>TRAIL BEM VIVER LONGO \u2013 31KM<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>TRAIL BEM VIVER CURTO &#8211; 20KM<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>TRAIL BEM VIVER MINI &#8211; 14KM<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>CAMINHADA BEM VIVER \u2013 10KM<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":47795,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"zakra_ge